<DocsLayout title="buoy history" description="View scan history and trends">
  <h1>buoy history</h1>

  <p>
    View scan history and track design system health over time. Compare
    scans to see progress and regressions.
  </p>

  <h2>Usage</h2>

  <pre><code>buoy history [command] [options]</code></pre>

  <h2>Commands</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Command</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td>(default)</td>
        <td>List recent scans</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>show &lt;scan-id&gt;</code></td>
        <td>Show details of a specific scan</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>compare &lt;scan1&gt; &lt;scan2&gt;</code></td>
        <td>Compare two scans</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Options</h2>

  <table>
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Option</th>
        <th>Description</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <tr>
        <td><code>--json</code></td>
        <td>Output as JSON</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>-n, --limit &lt;number&gt;</code></td>
        <td>Number of scans to show (default: 10)</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td><code>-v, --verbose</code></td>
        <td>Show detailed information</td>
      </tr>
    </tbody>
  </table>

  <h2>Examples</h2>

  <h3>List recent scans</h3>

  <pre><code>$ buoy history

Recent Scans
────────────────────────────────────────
ID       Date         Drift   Coverage
abc123   2024-01-15   23      72%
def456   2024-01-14   25      71%
ghi789   2024-01-13   28      69%</code></pre>

  <h3>Show scan details</h3>

  <pre><code>$ buoy history show abc123

Scan: abc123
Date: 2024-01-15 14:32:00
Duration: 2.3s

Results:
  Components: 42
  Tokens: 67
  Drift signals: 23
  Coverage: 72%

Top issues:
  - hardcoded-color: 12
  - hardcoded-spacing: 8
  - naming-inconsistency: 3</code></pre>

  <h3>Compare scans</h3>

  <pre><code>$ buoy history compare abc123 def456

Comparing abc123 → def456

Coverage: 71% → 72% (+1%)
Drift: 25 → 23 (-2)

Fixed:
  - Card.tsx:8 hardcoded-color
  - Badge.tsx:3 hardcoded-spacing

New:
  (none)</code></pre>

